column16: Adrian Beltre grounds into double play, shortstop Brendan Ryan to second baseman Munenori Kawasaki to first baseman Justin Smoak.    Josh Hamilton out at 2nd.
Josh Hamilton singles on a line drive to center fielder Michael Saunders.
Elvis Andrus grounds out softly, third baseman Kyle Seager to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Ian Kinsler homers (2) on a fly ball to left field.   Mike Napoli scores.    Mitch Moreland scores.
Mitch Moreland singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.    Mike Napoli to 2nd.
Craig Gentry grounds out to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Kila Ka'aihue singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.    Josh Donaldson to 2nd.
Josh Donaldson singles on a line drive to center fielder Michael Saunders.
Josh Reddick homers (1) on a fly ball to right field.
